                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I tend to haste but not dual wield charmed pets in Vxed/Tipt groups - it's overkill until the end boss, and quad rounds increase the chance of getting fatally stunned when charm breaks while I'm out pulling and the pet warps to me, or when it breaks in the middle of a fight and goes after someone else in group.
<br />

<br />
We use player tanks, using pets to tank runs the risk of charm breaking on a summoning mob which is generally followed by very quick death. With a good warrior I can land either a tash or a slow attempt, but not both, at 70% or so.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=308116" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ceranai</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
