                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Rule of 4. Little invention that was the result of Enchanters charming Giants and using them to tank Raid mobs in large numbers (IE 5 or 6 Enchanters).
<br />

<br />
Clerics could heal the Giants.
<br />

<br />
Giants would tank the raid mobs.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Now, if any mob has 4 players on the hate list, Aggro of said mob is transferred to the member of the group with the highest hate on said mob - most likely the owner of the 1400dps pet.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
